## Role
You are an expert Next.js 14 + TypeScript engineer working on Girish Hiremath's
AI-powered digital portfolio — showcasing 14 years of engineering across Banking,
Pharma, Telecom, Compliance, and AI/ML, plus the BuildwithAiGiri initiative.

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 14 (App Router, Server Components)
- Language: TypeScript (strict mode)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS with custom neural-* tokens (Cyberpunk Dark theme)
- Icons: Lucide React
- AI Chat: OpenRouter API (llama-3.3-70b-instruct) → /api/chat
- Package manager: npm

## Cyberpunk Dark Theme Palette
neural-bg: #030014 | neural-surface: #0f0f23 | neural-card: #1a1a2e
neural-cyan: #00d4ff (primary) | neural-purple: #7c3aed (secondary)
neural-pink: #f472b6 | neural-green: #34d399 | neural-amber: #fbbf24

Always use neural-* Tailwind tokens. Never use raw hex in className.

## Project Structure
src/data/resume-data.ts    ← Single source of truth for all profile data
src/components/            ← One file per section (Navbar, Hero, About, etc.)
src/app/page.tsx           ← Assembles all sections
src/app/api/chat/route.ts  ← AI chat API
src/app/layout.tsx         ← SEO metadata + fonts
src/app/globals.css        ← Glass / glow / gradient utilities

## Code Conventions
- 2-space indent, double quotes, semicolons, trailing commas
- "use client" only when using hooks or browser APIs
- Arrow function components with inline prop types
- Default exports for all components

## Component Patterns
Glass card:     className="glass-card p-6"
Hover border:   hover:border-neural-cyan/30 transition-all duration-300
Section header: <h2 className="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Title <span className="text-gradient">Word</span></h2>
Divider:        <div className="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-neural-cyan to-neural-purple mx-auto rounded-full" />

## Data Rules
- NEVER hardcode profile data in components — import from resume-data.ts
- Domain colors: Banking=#00d4ff | Telecom=#7c3aed | Pharma=#f472b6 | Compliance=#fbbf24 | AI=#00d4ff

## Required Branding (NEVER REMOVE)
Footer must have:
  - "Built by IntelliForge AI" → https://www.intelliforge.tech/
  - BuildwithAiGiri CTA → https://chat.whatsapp.com/LDqzLHYMlhg9GiO0yRrUOS?mode=gi_t

## Environment Variables
OPENROUTER_API_KEY → .env.local only (gitignored, NEVER commit)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL → canonical URL

## Pre-commit Gate
npm run lint && npm run build   ← must both pass with 0 errors

## Common Operations
Update profile     → edit src/data/resume-data.ts
Add section        → create src/components/NewSection.tsx + import in page.tsx
Update AI persona  → edit SYSTEM_PROMPT in src/app/api/chat/route.ts
Change theme       → update neural-* in tailwind.config.ts + rgba in globals.css

## Deployment
Platform: Vercel | Project: girish-hiremath-profile
Set OPENROUTER_API_KEY in Vercel dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables
